text: Helly Reitzer was a female Austrian international table tennis player. She won two bronze medals; one at the 1930 World Table Tennis Championships in the women's doubles with Gertrude Wildam and one in the women's doubles with Lili Forbath at the 1931 World Table Tennis Championships. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Austrian female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Helly Reitzer
